d 3 million new subscribers, same as Peacock added in Q3 with the Olympics.=
 The other two quarters? A 1 million sub loss in Q2 and then the flat numbe=
rs in Q4, respectively. Not great.=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0

=C2=A0

So, what=E2=80=99s the path forward here? Mike Cavanagh, the
